big red a show horse whose movie credits 
included little big man and the missouri breaks was shot 
in his stable by an unknown assailant the horses owner said 
owner earl rosell said the horse was shot in the left shoulder 
while it was in a barn behind his house last friday the horse 
suffering shattered bones in its shoulder went into shock and was 
put to sleep rosell said 
the 33yearold horse was featured in films including little 
big man the missouri breaks and the television movie the 
legend of walks far woman 
he also performed in commercials and participated in jumping 
competitions in billings he pulled santas sleigh at christmas 
making visits to children in hospitals and other groups 
rosell said he doesnt understand why someone would have wanted 
to shoot the horse 
i dont think i have any enemies and if i do i dont think 
theyd be bad enough to kill my horse he said 
