that he hates the united states which sought his extradition 
hamadi is charged with air piracy and murder in the june 1985 
hijacking of twa flight 847 to beirut thirtynine americans were 
held captive for 17 days and a us navy diver was killed during 
the ordeal 
west german federal police investigator heinrich brandtjen said 
hamadi admitted joining the radical hezbollah group after the twa 
hijacking 
hamadi was arrested and charged with carrying liquid explosives 
at frankfurt airport in 1987 
he told me he has belonged to hezbollah since the autumn of 
1985 or 1986 but i cannot remember exactly the year brandtjen 
told the court 
hezbollah or party of god is believed to be the umbrella 
organization for proiranian groups holding 18 foreign hostages in 
lebanon including nine americans hamadi denied last week that he 
had been a member of hezbollah 
one of hamadis brothers abdulhadi hamadi is the beirut 
