holds a libyan passport led the guerrilla attack 
police had also identified jaballa as taking part in the 
assassination of an egyptian newspaper editor in nicosia cyprus 
in 1978 he said 
jaballas fingerprints from cyprus were matched with those 
uncovered in his athens hideouts sehiotis said 
