but its the kind of interview thats going on dozens of times a 
day at the convention satellite news service the democratic 
partys equalopportunity showcase for tv stations too poor to come 
to the convention and politicians unlikely to show up on the 
network evening news 
thank you all this is a great thing youre wonderful youre 
wonderful sen tom harkin of iowa told the harried news service 
