stallings 
potential exists to carry many states stallings replied adding 
that dukakis is tremendously interested in trying to find out 
what our concerns are thats a first no other democrat has shown 
interest most tend to write off the west 
cut 
next in marched rep harold volkmer of missouri and the 
frantic pace a new face every five minutes continued 
this is insane kontnik said as she answered phone calls 
