of 15yearold nidal fuad rabadi who was shot to death in unclear 
circumstances tuesday near the jerusalem city limits 
police chief yosef yehudai said authorities had no leads in the 
shooting he said rabadi a jerusalem resident had been arrested 
four times in recent months for throwing stones at cars and buses 
both police and the army have denied involvement in the killing 
arab journalists said israelis driving to the west bank may have 
shot rabadi when firing at youths who threw rocks at their cars 
on wednesday police raided a house near the rabadi home and 
arrested 25 palestinians including some allegedly involved in the 
critical wounding of a border patrolman on tuesday 
